{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "防卫战～日出之国宝藏传说！～ 宝藏挖掘计划",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "在圣城伙伴们的帮助之下，\\n线索与证据接二连三地出土。\\n然而最终挖出黄金雕像后，\\n家康却发现这一切都是光秀的谎言，\\n遂质问光秀事情的真相。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "家康等人在井底发现了可疑的洞穴。\\n他们为了挖掘宝藏\\n而找来的帮手究竟是谁？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110356_01",
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "我从圣城带了几个\\n靠谱的家伙来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉辛",
            "context": "让你见识见识\\n宝藏猎人的本领吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110258_01",
                "110067_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维特",
            "context": "好了，赶快去寻宝吧！\\n宝藏♪宝藏♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120104_01",
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这里还有拉兹莉帮忙打造的\\n用来挖洞的工具。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "劳驾各位前来相助了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不用客气，\\n我们是自愿过来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "没错。寻找日出之国的宝藏\\n这种充满浪漫气息的事\\n可不能错过！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "家康这家伙，\\n喊来了这么多人啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "这就说明他是认真的。\\n何况能待在这里的时间有限。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "他认真到这种程度\\n反倒让我有些害怕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "嗯？你刚才说了什么吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "没有～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我坚信这洞穴深处\\n一定沉睡着历史的真相。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "为了探明真相，\\n恳请大家祝我一臂之力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "于是，宝藏挖掘计划正式启动。\\n家康与圣城的好手们\\n组成的挖掘团队\\n不断深入洞穴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "宝藏一定就在洞穴之中——\\n所有人都满怀希望。\\n仿佛是在回应众人的期待，\\n令人难以置信的东西接连被挖出……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，拉辛找到了这种东西。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "这是陶器的碎片，\\n从形状上来看\\n应该是碗的一部分。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "是挖洞的家伙\\n吃饭时用的饭碗吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "（哦？刚才那是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "皮多特也找到了什么！\\n大家快来看看！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "碗、生锈的工具和腐朽的木片……\\n这些东西是否与宝藏有所关联？\\n挖掘团队对于接连出土的线索\\n感到兴奋不已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "另一方面，为了帮助挖掘团队，\\n拉兹莉正运用罗卡族的技艺\\n研发着秘密武器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "这东西就是钻头吗？\\n能用来干什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120104_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "这个啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "魔力驱动下高速旋转的刀刃，\\n无论多坚硬的岩石\\n都能粉碎！厉害吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你身为龙\\n会讨厌这种机器吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "我可不像其他家伙们那样\\n整天在意这些鸡毛蒜皮的事。\\n而且我肯定比这玩意厉害。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120104_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "这个是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不不不，这可不一定哦？\\n魔力的量会影响这东西的威力，\\n说不定……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120104_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉兹莉",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "你给那家伙也讲讲吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "尽管盯上宝藏的帝国军\\n不停地向营地发起进攻，\\n但宝藏挖掘工作\\n决不会停歇！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "下、下次一定\\n不让你们有好果子吃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01",
                "120018_01",
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "壮硕的村民",
            "context": "哎呀，伤得这么厉害！\\n快来我们村休息休息吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "怎、怎么又是你们这群家伙！\\n每次都成群结队地涌上来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "浅薄的帝国兵",
            "context": "不过住的地方虽然破了点，\\n但服务的确非常周到啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "轻浮的帝国兵",
            "context": "是啊，旅馆的姑娘也很可爱♪\\n我们还是听他们的，\\n在这里养精蓄锐吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军队长",
            "context": "喂！你们几个！等等！\\n别丢下我啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "那些家伙真是不长记性～\\n唉，累死我了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村长",
            "context": "不过，像这样每次来村里休息\\n让我们能挣到钱，我们也很高兴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村长",
            "context": "最近你们寻宝的事已经传开了，\\n因此来了很多对传说感兴趣的游客，\\n村里现在可热闹了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村长",
            "context": "真的是非常感谢。\\n多亏了您，我们村才能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "要安心还为时过早。\\n“天岩户计划”差不多\\n也该进入下一阶段了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "休息一下吧。\\n虽然挖出了很多像样的线索，\\n却始终不见关键的宝藏啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "是啊，不过能发现我的先祖……\\n“狐狸”可能存在的线索，\\n还是让我很欣慰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你的心情我可以理解。\\n这种很久以前的人似乎\\n触手可及的感觉总是让人激动嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不过那个叫“狐狸”的家伙\\n有可能偷了军费吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "要了解事情的真相之后\\n才能对他进行评价，我认为\\n这是对已故先祖应有的尊敬。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "如果这次找到了他是罪人的证据，\\n我定会以此为戒牢记过去的教训。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "而若他是被冤枉的，\\n那为其洗刷冤屈\\n自然是我身为子孙的责任。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "对已故之人的尊敬吗，\\n你果然是个老好人啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "话说戈尔德有提到过\\n对挖洞穴的人的见解，\\n不知道对你有没有帮助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那洞穴里用石墙加固的\\n只有入口的部分对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "也就是说为当初了不让洞穴坍塌，\\n原本有在用石墙加固，但后来\\n可能是因为原料不足而放弃了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "即便如此也不顾随时会坍塌的危险\\n而继续挖掘的话，应该是有什么\\n能让人奋不顾身的理由。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "奋不顾身的理由吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "喂～家康～洞穴深处\\n发现了不得了的东西哦～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢，你来啦。快看这个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "这……这是！？\\n黄金打造的龙雕像？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "厉害了！这不会就是\\n宝藏的一部分吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210156_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "摩利支天",
            "context": "按家康氏族中流传的说法，\\n被掳走的军费应该是金条吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "口口相传的故事本身就不可靠。\\n总之这样一来，洞穴深处埋藏着\\n宝藏的可能性一下子就高起来了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "确实如此……\\n不过，这雕像……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "时候也不早了，明天再继续吧。\\n既然找到了这黄金雕像，\\n我们就好好庆祝一番吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "那我去找村长借用一下餐厅，\\n大家一起过去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "马蒂殿下，请稍等。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110261_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马蒂",
            "context": "怎么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我有一个不情之请。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "当天晚上……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "果然是你在捣鬼吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "次日清晨……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "呼……呼……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "光秀，该起床了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了，家康？\\n让我再多睡一会儿～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "有一件事要问你。\\n我让马蒂殿下帮忙鉴定了\\n昨天出土的黄金雕像。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "结果那雕像只是表面裹着金箔，\\n里面却是由木头制成。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "而且据说那雕像\\n是最近才制作完成的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "咦，是这样吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "不仅如此。因为变成了金色\\n所以我没能立刻发现，\\n但我对那雕像有印象。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "我到访你的领地之时……\\n在特产店里见过那雕像。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "那尊假的黄金雕像其实\\n是你埋下去的吧，光秀？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22214_03_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}